        United Kingdom

        %p.govuk-body
          Email:
          = link_to "enquiries@beis.gov.uk", "mailto:enquiries@beis.gov.uk", class: "govuk-link"

        %p.govuk-body
          Telephone:
          = link_to "020 7215 5000", "tel:+442072155000", class: "govuk-link"

      %p.govuk-body
        Monday to Friday, 9am to 4:30pm

      %h2.govuk-heading-m
        Changes to this policy

      %p.govuk-body
        We may change this privacy policy. In that case, the ‘last updated’ date at the bottom of this page will also change. Any changes to this privacy policy will apply to you and your data immediately.

      %p.govuk-body
        If these changes affect how your personal data is processed, BEIS will take reasonable steps to let you know.

      %p.govuk-body
        Last updated: 2 April 2020
